```

---

## 2. CSS (MCSS — Component Layer)

```css
/* ============================================
   c-button — Atom
   Layer: Component (c-*)
   ============================================ */

.c-button {
  /* ---- Layout & Box ---- */
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: var(--space-2);
  padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-5);
  border: 2px solid transparent;
  border-radius: var(--border-radius-md);
  cursor: pointer;

  /* ---- Typography ---- */
  font-family: var(--font-family-sans);
  font-size: var(--font-size-body);
  font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);
  line-height: var(--line-height-base);
  text-decoration: none;
  white-space: nowrap;
  user-select: none;

  /* ---- Visual ---- */
  background-color: transparent;
  color: inherit;
  transition:
    background-color var(--transition-fast),
    color var(--transition-fast),
    border-color var(--transition-fast),
    box-shadow var(--transition-fast);

  /* ---- Accessibility ---- */
  outline-offset: 2px;
}

/* ---- Variants (via data-variant) ---- */

/* Primary */
.c-button[data-variant="primary"] {
  background-color: var(--color-background-brand);
  color: var(--color-text-on-brand);
  border-color: var(--color-background-brand);
}
.c-button[data-variant="primary"]:hover,
.c-button[data-variant="primary"]:focus-visible {
  background-color: var(--color-background-brand-hover);
  border-color: var(--color-background-brand-hover);
}

/* Secondary */
.c-button[data-variant="secondary"] {
  background-color: var(--color-background-secondary);
  color: var(--color-text-primary);
  border-color: var(--color-border-interactive);
}
.c-button[data-variant="secondary"]:hover,
.c-button[data-variant="secondary"]:focus-visible {
  background-color: var(--color-gray-100);
  border-color: var(--color-brand-500);
}

/* Outline */
.c-button[data-variant="outline"] {
  background-color: transparent;
  color: var(--color-text-link);
  border-color: var(--color-border-interactive);
}
.c-button[data-variant="outline"]:hover,
.c-button[data-variant="outline"]:focus-visible {
  background-color: var(--color-brand-50);
  border-color: var(--color-brand-500);
}

/* Ghost */
.c-button[data-variant="ghost"] {
  background-color: transparent;
  color: var(--color-text-link);
  border-color: transparent;
}
.c-button[data-variant="ghost"]:hover,
.c-button[data-variant="ghost"]:focus-visible {
  background-color: var(--color-brand-50);
}

/* ---- States (via data-state) ---- */

/* Loading */
.c-button[data-state="loading"] {
  pointer-events: none;
  opacity: 0.7;
}
.c-button[data-state="loading"] .c-button__spinner {
  display: inline-flex;
}
.c-button[data-state="loading"] .c-button__label {
  opacity: 0.7;
}

/* Disabled */
.c-button[data-state="disabled"],
.c-button:disabled {
  pointer-events: none;
  opacity: 0.4;
  cursor: not-allowed;
}

/* Error */
.c-button[data-state="error"] {
  background-color: var(--color-background-error);
  color: var(--color-text-on-brand);
  border-color: var(--color-border-error);
}
.c-button[data-state="error"]:hover,
.c-button[data-state="error"]:focus-visible {
  background-color: var(--color-red-800);
  border-color: var(--color-red-800);
}

/* ---- Focus ring (all variants) ---- */
.c-button:focus-visible {
  outline: 2px solid var(--color-border-focus);
  outline-offset: 2px;
}

/* ---- Elements ---- */

.c-button__label {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: var(--space-1);
}

.c-button__spinner {
  display: none;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
}

/* ---- Icon support (optional) ---- */
.c-button .c-icon {
  width: 1em;
  height: 1em;
}
```

---

## 3. Usage Examples

```html
<!-- Primary (default) -->
<button class="c-button" data-variant="primary" data-state="default">Submit</button>

<!-- Secondary -->
<button class="c-button" data-variant="secondary" data-state="default">Cancel</button>

<!-- Outline -->
<button class="c-button" data-variant="outline" data-state="default">Learn More</button>

<!-- Ghost -->
<button class="c-button" data-variant="ghost" data-state="default">Dismiss</button>

<!-- Loading -->
<button class="c-button" data-variant="primary" data-state="loading">Saving…</button>

<!-- Disabled -->
<button class="c-button" data-variant="primary" data-state="disabled" disabled>Disabled</button>

<!-- Error -->
<button class="c-button" data-variant="primary" data-state="error">Retry</button>
```

---

## 4. Design Decisions

| Decision | Rationale |
|---|---|
| **`data-variant` for visual style** | Keeps the component taxonomy clean — variant is a visual axis, not a state. Follows ONC naming without polluting class modifiers. |
| **`data-state` for loading/disabled/error** | States are dynamic and behavioral. Using `data-state` aligns with the MCSS state management rule and enables JS-driven toggling without class manipulation. |
| **No margin on `.c-button`** | Golden Rule enforced — spacing is delegated to layout wrappers (`l-stack`, `l-cluster`). |
| **`gap` for icon/label spacing** | Uses `var(--space-2)` for consistent internal spacing between icon and label. |
| **`transition` on multiple properties** | Smooth visual feedback for hover, focus, and state changes. Uses `var(--transition-fast)` for snappy interactions. |
| **`outline-offset` + `focus-visible`** | Accessible focus ring that doesn't overlap the button border. |
| **Spinner as child element** | The `c-button__spinner` is hidden by default and shown only when `data-state="loading"`. This keeps the button size stable during state transitions. |
| **`pointer-events: none` on loading/disabled** | Prevents accidental clicks while preserving visual state for screen readers. |

---

## 5. Validation Checklist

- ✅ No magic numbers — all values use `var(--token)`
- ✅ Correct layer prefix (`c-`)
- ✅ No margin on root `.c-button` selector
- ✅ RDFa annotations present (`typeof`, `taxonomyLevel`, `purpose`)
- ✅ State via `data-state`, not class modifiers
- ✅ Every `var()` references a defined token from the compendium
- ✅ Variants via `data-variant` attribute
- ✅ Accessible focus ring with `focus-visible`
- ✅ Loading state hides label and shows spinner

