     property="mcs:taxonomyLevel" content="mcs:Molecule"
     property="mcs:purpose" content="Toggleable menu for selecting options"
     data-state="open"
     data-mcs-interaction-type="toggle"
     data-mcs-consequence="Shows or hides dropdown options"
     data-mcs-triggers-event="mcss:dropdown:toggled">

  <!-- Trigger Button -->
  <button 
    aria-haspopup="true"
    aria-expanded="true"
    aria-controls="dropdown-menu-1"
    id="dropdown-trigger-1"
    type="button">
    <span class="c-dropdown__label">Options</span>
    <span class="c-dropdown__icon" aria-hidden="true">▼</span>
  </button>

  <!-- Menu Panel -->
  <ul 
    id="dropdown-menu-1"
    role="menu"
    aria-labelledby="dropdown-trigger-1"
    class="c-dropdown__menu">
    <li role="none">
      <button role="menuitem" tabindex="-1">Option 1</button>
    </li>
    <li role="none">
      <button role="menuitem" tabindex="-1">Option 2</button>
    </li>
  </ul>
</div>
```

### Keyboard Navigation

| Key | Action |
|---|---|
| **Enter/Space** (on trigger) | Toggle menu open/closed |
| **Escape** (when open) | Close menu, focus returns to trigger |
| **Arrow Down** (when open) | Move focus to next menu item |
| **Arrow Up** (when open) | Move focus to previous menu item |
| **Home** (when open) | Move focus to first menu item |
| **End** (when open) | Move focus to last menu item |
| **Tab** | Close menu, move to next focusable element |

### Focus Management

1. **On open**: Focus moves to first menu item
2. **On close**: Focus returns to trigger button
3. **On item selection**: Focus returns to trigger button
4. **Roving tabindex**: Only one menu item has `tabindex="0"` at a time

